Dialogue: 10,0:00:04.43,0:00:05.48,dialog,,0,0,0,,Contoh?
Dialogue: 10,0:00:05.48,0:00:10.31,dialog,,0,0,0,,Tepat. Aku merekam pembacaan Senior Mitsuka\Nsaat istirahat makan siang.
Dialogue: 10,0:00:10.31,0:00:12.27,dialog,,0,0,0,,Senior Mitsuka?
Dialogue: 10,0:00:12.27,0:00:15.49,dialog,,0,0,0,,Orang yang juara pertama\Nkategori siaran tingkat Kyoto itu, ya?
Dialogue: 10,0:00:16.21,0:00:19.24,dialog,,0,0,0,,Orang yang maju ke tingkat nasional\Nsaat kelas satu itu, ya?
Dialogue: 10,0:00:19.24,0:00:22.05,dialog,,0,0,0,,Betul, betul. Senior Mitsuka yang itu!
Dialogue: 10,0:00:22.05,0:00:24.45,dialog,,0,0,0,,Ini. Coba dengarkan.
Dialogue: 10,0:00:24.45,0:00:26.17,dialog,,0,0,0,,Terima kasih.
Dialogue: 10,0:00:30.43,0:00:32.67,dialog,,0,0,0,,Malam berikutnya,
Dialogue: 10,0:00:32.67,0:00:36.93,dialog,,0,0,0,,Gauche kembali pulang sembari\Nmembawa bungkusan selo hitam di pundaknya.
Dialogue: 10,0:00:37.35,0:00:40.00,dialog,,0,0,0,,Setelah meneguk air minum,
Dialogue: 10,0:00:40.00,0:00:45.16,dialog,,0,0,0,,dia mulai memainkan selo\Npersis seperti kemarin malam.
Dialogue: 10,0:00:46.45,0:00:48.51,dialog,,0,0,0,,Benar-benar mahir, ya.
Dialogue: 10,0:00:48.51,0:00:50.07,dialog,,0,0,0,,Setuju.
Dialogue: 10,0:00:50.23,0:00:52.82,dialog,,0,0,0,,Aku akan mengikuti contoh ini.
Dialogue: 10,0:00:54.93,0:00:56.53,dialog,,0,0,0,,Malam berikutnya,
Dialogue: 10,0:00:56.53,0:01:01.42,dialog,,0,0,0,,Gauche kembali pulang sembari\Nmembawa bungkusan selo hitam di pundaknya.
Dialogue: 10,0:01:01.44,0:01:04.04,dialog,,0,0,0,,Setelah meneguk air minum,
Dialogue: 10,0:01:04.04,0:01:09.13,dialog,,0,0,0,,dia mulai memainkan selo\Npersis seperti kemarin malam.
Dialogue: 10,0:01:11.16,0:01:13.27,dialog,,0,0,0,,Apa ada yang salah?
Dialogue: 10,0:01:14.80,0:01:19.47,dialog,,0,0,0,,Bagus, sih, tapi menurutku ada yang aneh.
Dialogue: 10,0:01:19.47,0:01:23.72,dialog,,0,0,0,,Rasanya, percuma saja ada kemajuan\Nkarena meniru orang lain.
Dialogue: 10,0:01:23.72,0:01:27.94,dialog,,0,0,0,,Apa kamu akan tetap mengatakan itu\Nsaat kalah dalam turnamen?
Dialogue: 10,0:01:28.61,0:01:32.40,dialog,,0,0,0,,Hanya enam orang yang bisa maju\Nke tingkat nasional kategori monolog, lo.
Dialogue: 10,0:01:32.40,0:01:34.86,dialog,,0,0,0,,Sudah begitu, kita ini baru kelas satu!
Dialogue: 10,0:01:34.86,0:01:36.90,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kalau ingin lebih mahir\Ndalam waktu terbatas,
Dialogue: 10,0:01:36.90,0:01:39.54,dialog,,0,0,0,,jangan banyak gengsi!
Dialogue: 10,0:01:39.54,0:01:42.83,dialog,,0,0,0,,Perkataan Xiang Ling ada benarnya.
Dialogue: 10,0:01:42.84,0:01:44.60,dialog,,0,0,0,,Meski meniru secara keseluruhan\Nagak berlebihan,
Dialogue: 10,0:01:44.63,0:01:48.04,dialog,,0,0,0,,tapi latihan dengan meniru senior\Nitu wajar.
Dialogue: 10,0:01:48.24,0:01:50.08,dialog,,0,0,0,,Apa iya?
Dialogue: 10,0:01:50.08,0:01:51.36,dialog,,0,0,0,,Jangan banyak alasan,
Dialogue: 10,0:01:51.36,0:01:54.80,dialog,,0,0,0,,Hana juga harusnya\Ncuri hal bagus dari senior.
Dialogue: 10,0:01:54.80,0:01:59.39,dialog,,0,0,0,,Sebaiknya kamu minta pendapat dari senior\Nsupaya bisa makin mahir.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:32.17,0:03:33.25,dialog,,0,0,0,,Senior!
Dialogue: 10,0:03:34.86,0:03:39.07,dialog,,0,0,0,,Tolong ajarkan Hana\Ncara meningkatkan teknik pembacaan.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:40.77,0:03:42.57,dialog,,0,0,0,,Mo-Mohon bantuannya!
Dialogue: 10,0:03:42.57,0:03:44.82,dialog,,0,0,0,,Dengan senang hati.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:46.09,0:03:48.58,dialog,,0,0,0,,Coba baca dulu.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:48.58,0:03:50.79,dialog,,0,0,0,,Ba-Baik.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:53.61,0:03:55.13,dialog,,0,0,0,,Malam berikutnya,
Dialogue: 10,0:03:55.13,0:03:59.67,dialog,,0,0,0,,Gauche kembali pulang sembari\Nmembawa bungkusan selo hitam di pundaknya.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:59.67,0:04:02.53,dialog,,0,0,0,,Setelah meneguk air minum,
Dialogue: 10,0:04:02.53,0:04:05.39,dialog,,0,0,0,,dia mulai memainkan selo persis seperti...
Dialogue: 10,0:04:05.39,0:04:07.76,dialog,,0,0,0,,Imutnya!
Dialogue: 10,0:04:07.76,0:04:10.95,dialog,,0,0,0,,I-Itu... Imut yang bagaimana?
Dialogue: 10,0:04:10.95,0:04:13.63,dialog,,0,0,0,,Semuanya!
Dialogue: 10,0:04:15.13,0:04:18.48,dialog,,0,0,0,,Suaramu bagus, ya.\NJelas dan mudah didengar.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:18.48,0:04:22.11,dialog,,0,0,0,,Namun, kelompok usia pendengarnya\Nmungkin agak rendah.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:22.11,0:04:23.97,dialog,,0,0,0,,Jadi, ekspresinya sedikit berlebihan.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:23.97,0:04:25.89,dialog,,0,0,0,,Berlebihan?
Dialogue: 10,0:04:25.89,0:04:27.87,dialog,,0,0,0,,Misalnya...
Dialogue: 10,0:04:28.19,0:04:31.55,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kalau aku minta kamu peragakan\N"hujan yang turun",
Dialogue: 10,0:04:31.55,0:04:32.64,dialog,,0,0,0,,kamu akan lakukan apa?
Dialogue: 10,0:04:32.65,0:04:34.38,dialog,,0,0,0,,Hujan?
Dialogue: 10,0:04:34.93,0:04:38.25,dialog,,0,0,0,,"Bres, bres!" seperti itu?
Dialogue: 10,0:04:39.35,0:04:41.01,dialog,,0,0,0,,Hana, kamu imut banget.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:42.17,0:04:45.80,dialog,,0,0,0,,Yang sederhana saja cukup, lo.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:53.77,0:04:54.83,dialog,,0,0,0,,Paham?
Dialogue: 10,0:04:54.83,0:04:57.13,dialog,,0,0,0,,Apa kubilang?\NPokoko hebat, 'kan?
Dialogue: 10,0:04:57.13,0:04:58.91,dialog,,0,0,0,,Membaca juga sama.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:58.91,0:05:02.83,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kamu bisa menampilkan ekspresi berbeda\Ndengan sedikit mengubah cara bicaramu.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:02.83,0:05:06.69,dialog,,0,0,0,,Karena itu, lebih baik pelajari\Nartikulasi yang tepat dulu,
Dialogue: 10,0:05:06.69,0:05:10.43,dialog,,0,0,0,,baru kemudian pikirkan ekspresinya.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:10.43,0:05:12.75,dialog,,0,0,0,,Artikulasi yang tepat saat membaca...
Dialogue: 10,0:05:12.75,0:05:15.31,dialog,,0,0,0,,Nah, coba baca sekali lagi.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:15.31,0:05:16.50,dialog,,0,0,0,,Baik.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:16.50,0:05:18.25,dialog,,0,0,0,,Malam berikutnya,
Dialogue: 10,0:05:18.25,0:05:22.17,dialog,,0,0,0,,Gauche kembali pulang sembari\Nmembawa bungkusan selo hitam di pundaknya.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:22.17,0:05:24.49,dialog,,0,0,0,,Bunyi "gi" dalam "tsugi"\Nadalah konsonan sengau.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:24.49,0:05:27.87,dialog,,0,0,0,,Lalu, kata setelah "gi"\Ndilafalkan lebih rendah, ya.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:27.87,0:05:29.15,dialog,,0,0,0,,Malam berikutnya,
Dialogue: 10,0:05:29.15,0:05:33.29,dialog,,0,0,0,,Gauche kembali pulang sembari\Nmembawa bungkusan selo hitam di pundaknya.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:33.29,0:05:35.95,dialog,,0,0,0,,Bunyi "tsu" dalam "tsutsumi" dilafalkan\Nseolah tidak ada huruf vokal.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:35.95,0:05:37.25,dialog,,0,0,0,,Hati-hati, ya.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:37.25,0:05:38.55,dialog,,0,0,0,,Malam berikutnya,
Dialogue: 10,0:05:38.55,0:05:42.59,dialog,,0,0,0,,Gauche kembali pulang sembari\Nmembawa bungkusan selo hitam di pundaknya.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:42.59,0:05:44.93,dialog,,0,0,0,,Oh, sudah bagus!
Dialogue: 10,0:05:44.93,0:05:46.15,dialog,,0,0,0,,Malam berikutnya,
Dialogue: 10,0:05:46.15,0:05:50.45,dialog,,0,0,0,,Gauche kembali pulang sembari\Nmembawa bungkusan selo hitam di pundaknya.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:50.45,0:05:53.15,dialog,,0,0,0,,Wah, yang sebelumnya lebih bagus.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:53.15,0:05:55.11,dialog,,0,0,0,,Bagian "tsugi"-nya kembali ke awal.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:55.11,0:05:57.35,dialog,,0,0,0,,Boleh baca satu kali lagi?
Dialogue: 10,0:05:57.35,0:05:58.71,dialog,,0,0,0,,Ba-Baik.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:59.47,0:06:00.45,dialog,,0,0,0,,Eng...
Dialogue: 10,0:06:00.45,0:06:02.53,dialog,,0,0,0,,Yang barusan tidak tepat,
Dialogue: 10,0:06:02.53,0:06:04.53,dialog,,0,0,0,,yang ketiga sudah bagus.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:04.53,0:06:06.47,dialog,,0,0,0,,Bunyi "tsu" dalam "tsugi"\Ntidak perlu dibaca tanpa vokal.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:07.05,0:06:09.22,dialog,,0,0,0,,Jadi, pelafalannya beda dengan "tsu"\Ndalam "tsutsumi"...
Dialogue: 10,0:06:09.91,0:06:12.22,dialog,,0,0,0,,Setelah itu...
Dialogue: 10,0:06:12.83,0:06:14.07,dialog,,0,0,0,,Malam berikutnya,
Dialogue: 10,0:06:14.07,0:06:15.22,dialog,,0,0,0,,Gauche kembali...
Dialogue: 10,0:06:15.49,0:06:16.73,dialog,,0,0,0,,Sebentar...
Dialogue: 10,0:06:16.98,0:06:19.73,dialog,,0,0,0,,Bagaimana caraku membaca ini tadi?
Dialogue: 10,0:06:19.73,0:06:20.73,dialog,,0,0,0,,Hana.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:20.95,0:06:22.86,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kamu baik-baik saja?
Dialogue: 10,0:06:30.63,0:06:34.23,dialog,,0,0,0,,Ini, minum sesuatu yang manis\Ndan istirahat sebentar.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:34.23,0:06:36.83,dialog,,0,0,0,,Terima kasih.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:43.25,0:06:45.71,dialog,,0,0,0,,Wajar saja kalau kamu cemas.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:45.71,0:06:50.31,dialog,,0,0,0,,Padahal sebentar lagi turnamen,\Ntapi tiba-tiba dikasih tahu macam-macam.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:50.31,0:06:52.42,dialog,,0,0,0,,Oh, tidak...
Dialogue: 10,0:06:53.43,0:06:56.63,dialog,,0,0,0,,Telingaku juga sakit\Nsaat mendengar arahan Pokoko.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:56.63,0:06:59.16,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kemampuan membaca dengan teknik\Nyang sama persis itu
Dialogue: 10,0:06:59.16,0:07:01.33,dialog,,0,0,0,,tidak bisa dikuasai dalam satu malam.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:01.33,0:07:04.15,dialog,,0,0,0,,Karena itu, Pokoko dan Mitsuka itu hebat.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:04.55,0:07:07.27,dialog,,0,0,0,,Aku juga harus berusaha supaya tidak kalah.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:07.27,0:07:09.55,dialog,,0,0,0,,A-Aku juga akan berusaha!
Dialogue: 10,0:07:11.11,0:07:13.37,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kamu tidak perlu setegang itu.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:13.75,0:07:16.55,dialog,,0,0,0,,Menurutku, Hana selalu berusaha keras, kok.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:17.87,0:07:24.09,dialog,,0,0,0,,Baiklah, aku akan kembali ke kelas.\NHana cari angin dulu saja, ya?
Dialogue: 10,0:07:24.99,0:07:26.99,dialog,,0,0,0,,Baiklah.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:33.39,0:07:37.85,dialog,,0,0,0,,Aku juga ingin menjadi orang\Nseperti Senior Mizuki.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:38.97,0:07:41.02,dialog,,0,0,0,,Aku ingin lebih mahir dalam membaca,
Dialogue: 10,0:07:41.03,0:07:44.35,dialog,,0,0,0,,dan maju ke tingkat nasional\Nbersama Senior...
Dialogue: 10,0:07:44.35,0:07:46.86,dialog,,0,0,0,,Bukankah itu mustahil?
Dialogue: 10,0:07:53.01,0:07:55.79,dialog,,0,0,0,,Maaf, itu...
Dialogue: 10,0:07:57.21,0:08:00.75,dialog,,0,0,0,,Aku lupa sudah melepaskan kacamata tadi.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:02.51,0:08:04.46,dialog,,0,0,0,,Namaku Hiiragidani Mitsuka.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:06.33,0:08:08.33,dialog,,0,0,0,,Sa-Salam kenal.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:08.33,0:08:11.93,dialog,,0,0,0,,Aku Haruyama Hana,\Nsiswi kelas satu SMA Sumomogaoka.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:11.94,0:08:12.44,dialog,,0,0,0,,Itu...
Dialogue: 10,0:08:13.19,0:08:14.97,dialog,,0,0,0,,Maksudnya mustahil yang barusan itu...?
Dialogue: 10,0:08:14.97,0:08:17.29,dialog,,0,0,0,,Bagaimana pendapatmu\Ntentang pembacaan Usurai?
Dialogue: 10,0:08:17.29,0:08:18.51,dialog,,0,0,0,,"Bagaimana"?
Dialogue: 10,0:08:18.91,0:08:21.68,dialog,,0,0,0,,Dia selalu terlihat keren.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:21.89,0:08:24.52,dialog,,0,0,0,,Suaranya bagus dan tidak monoton.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:25.81,0:08:29.28,dialog,,0,0,0,,Aku yakin Senior Mizuki\Nbisa maju ke tingkat nasional.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:30.43,0:08:33.21,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kamu ini sangat menyukai Usurai, ya.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:33.21,0:08:34.91,dialog,,0,0,0,,Eh, begitulah...
Dialogue: 10,0:08:34.91,0:08:37.43,dialog,,0,0,0,,Jadi, kamu ingin pergi\Nke tingkat nasional bersamanya?
Dialogue: 10,0:08:37.43,0:08:38.24,dialog,,0,0,0,,Eh?
Dialogue: 10,0:08:38.24,0:08:41.11,dialog,,0,0,0,,Sepertinya kamu masih belum paham, ya.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:41.11,0:08:44.25,dialog,,0,0,0,,Oh, ralat.\NMungkin lebih tepat "tidak mau" paham.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:44.63,0:08:46.88,dialog,,0,0,0,,So-Soal apa?
Dialogue: 10,0:08:49.13,0:08:52.88,dialog,,0,0,0,,Soal kamu sebenarnya saingan Usurai.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:59.21,0:09:01.89,dialog,,0,0,0,,Persaingan dan mengagumi itu\Ndua hal yang berbeda.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:01.89,0:09:04.75,dialog,,0,0,0,,Jika kamu juga benar-benar\Ningin maju ke tingkat nasional,
Dialogue: 10,0:09:04.75,0:09:07.98,dialog,,0,0,0,,bagaimana kalau kamu membulatkan\Ntekad untuk melawan senior?
Dialogue: 10,0:09:10.29,0:09:11.19,dialog,,0,0,0,,Itu...
Dialogue: 10,0:09:11.68,0:09:16.74,dialog,,0,0,0,,Apa Senior Hiiragidani sudah\Nmembulatkan tekad sejak kelas satu?
Dialogue: 10,0:09:19.74,0:09:21.20,dialog,,0,0,0,,Tentu saja.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:21.79,0:09:25.71,dialog,,0,0,0,,Karena aku adalah andalan\NAkademi Putri Lilac.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:26.15,0:09:29.29,dialog,,0,0,0,,Baiklah, aku permisi.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:35.79,0:09:38.39,dialog,,0,0,0,,Apa aku harus memikirkan kemenangan?
Dialogue: 10,0:09:38.39,0:09:41.97,dialog,,0,0,0,,Hanya kemenangan\Nyang mampu memuaskan aku.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:43.15,0:09:46.81,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kamu bohong soal tidak ingin menang, 'kan?
Dialogue: 10,0:09:57.98,0:10:00.05,dialog,,0,0,0,,Koleksi kerajinan tradisional
Dialogue: 10,0:10:00.05,0:10:03.28,dialog,,0,0,0,,seperti tembikar dan tekstil\Nyang diwarnai akan dipamerkan dalam
Dialogue: 10,0:10:03.29,0:10:06.69,dialog,,0,0,0,,"Pameran Kerajinan Tradisional"\Npada tanggal 16 di Kota Maizuru.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:08.69,0:10:10.71,dialog,,0,0,0,,Natsue.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:12.09,0:10:14.46,dialog,,0,0,0,,Suaramu keren sekali.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:14.67,0:10:17.73,dialog,,0,0,0,,Namun, ada beberapa bagian\Nyang terdengar seperti robot.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:17.73,0:10:21.13,dialog,,0,0,0,,Ada baiknya kalau kamu\Nmemikirkan posisi pendengar juga.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:21.29,0:10:23.29,dialog,,0,0,0,,Terima kasih.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:23.29,0:10:26.73,dialog,,0,0,0,,Selagi di sini, bagaimana kalau membaca\Nbersama dengan murid sekolah lain?
Dialogue: 10,0:10:28.03,0:10:28.94,dialog,,0,0,0,,Chiaki.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:29.88,0:10:31.27,dialog,,0,0,0,,Sini, sini.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:32.23,0:10:34.69,dialog,,0,0,0,,Chiaki adalah adikku dan Manaka.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:34.69,0:10:38.53,dialog,,0,0,0,,Tahun lalu, dia juara tiga kategori siaran,\Nkamu bisa tanya macam-macam padanya.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:42.21,0:10:46.04,dialog,,0,0,0,,Aku Hayashi Chiaki,\Nsiswi kelas 3 SMA Chizuru.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:46.27,0:10:47.47,dialog,,0,0,0,,Itu...
Dialogue: 10,0:10:47.47,0:10:49.54,dialog,,0,0,0,,Apa ada yang mau kamu tanyakan?
Dialogue: 10,0:10:50.05,0:10:55.05,dialog,,0,0,0,,Daripada bertanya, lebih tepatnya Bu Monaka\Nyang memanggilmu secara sepihak.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:55.05,0:10:56.92,dialog,,0,0,0,,Be-Begitu, ya.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:57.33,0:10:59.80,dialog,,0,0,0,,Maaf, kakakku sudah membuatmu tidak nyaman.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:59.80,0:11:03.93,dialog,,0,0,0,,Daripada aku, bagaimana kalau\Nminta tolong Hiiragidani dari Lilac?
Dialogue: 10,0:11:03.93,0:11:05.71,dialog,,0,0,0,,Tidak, tidak perlu...
Dialogue: 10,0:11:05.71,0:11:08.56,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kebetulan Kak Hiiragidani...
Dialogue: 10,0:11:08.56,0:11:11.05,dialog,,0,0,0,,Sedang istirahat... mungkin?
Dialogue: 10,0:11:11.05,0:11:13.65,dialog,,0,0,0,,Mungkin dia pergi ke kelas monolog.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:13.65,0:11:15.13,dialog,,0,0,0,,Eh?
Dialogue: 10,0:11:15.13,0:11:19.32,dialog,,0,0,0,,Lilac punya tradisi menjadikan\Npembacaan senior sebagai contoh.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:19.71,0:11:24.53,dialog,,0,0,0,,Namun, Botanboko tidak suka\Ndijadikan sebagai contoh.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:24.53,0:11:26.86,dialog,,0,0,0,,Karena itu,\NHiiragidani-lah yang bertanggung jawab
Dialogue: 10,0:11:26.86,0:11:29.89,dialog,,0,0,0,,menjadi contoh\Nuntuk kategori monolog juga.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:29.89,0:11:32.17,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kenapa Senior tahu soal itu?
Dialogue: 10,0:11:33.11,0:11:36.21,dialog,,0,0,0,,Ketua ekskul kami, Nishino, yang cerita.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:37.09,0:11:42.17,dialog,,0,0,0,,Nishino itu lelaki yang netral,\Natau tidak terlalu berpengaruh.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:42.17,0:11:45.22,dialog,,0,0,0,,Namun, dia terkadang bisa diandalkan.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:45.47,0:11:48.56,dialog,,0,0,0,,Jangan-jangan... Senior menaksir dia, ya?
Dialogue: 10,0:11:48.56,0:11:50.57,dialog,,0,0,0,,Ko-Kok tertebak?
Dialogue: 10,0:11:50.57,0:11:52.96,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kelihatan jelas sekali.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:52.96,0:11:56.77,dialog,,0,0,0,,Namun, cinta ini tak terbalas.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:59.15,0:12:03.03,dialog,,0,0,0,,Karena Nishino menyukai Minohara.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:05.53,0:12:08.33,dialog,,0,0,0,,Aku paham perasaan Senior!
Dialogue: 10,0:12:24.03,0:12:26.11,dialog,,0,0,0,,Tekad, ya.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:29.17,0:12:30.87,dialog,,0,0,0,,Senior Hakoyama?
Dialogue: 10,0:12:31.68,0:12:33.61,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kenapa ada di sini?
Dialogue: 10,0:12:35.75,0:12:38.45,dialog,,0,0,0,,Aku kabur dari Nishino.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:38.59,0:12:43.85,dialog,,0,0,0,,Dia orangnya ramah, sih, tapi kalau ngobrol\Nsuka asyik sendiri. Aku jadi capek.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:44.99,0:12:48.04,dialog,,0,0,0,,Saat aku mengeluh ingin pulang di grup,
Dialogue: 10,0:12:48.04,0:12:50.83,dialog,,0,0,0,,Touga bilang dia akan datang menyusul.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:54.56,0:12:56.60,dialog,,0,0,0,,Pada latihan bersama kali ini,
Dialogue: 10,0:12:56.60,0:13:00.34,dialog,,0,0,0,,kita sudah belajar\Ntentang banyak hal selain teknik.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:00.66,0:13:03.59,dialog,,0,0,0,,Turnamen Kyoto sebentar lagi dimulai.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:03.59,0:13:06.97,dialog,,0,0,0,,Mari usahakan yang terbaik\Nagar tidak ada penyesalan.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:07.53,0:13:09.47,dialog,,0,0,0,,Baik!
Dialogue: 10,0:13:12.87,0:13:14.98,dialog,,0,0,0,,Mari sama-sama berusaha.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:14.98,0:13:17.43,dialog,,0,0,0,,Untuk turnamen dan juga...
Dialogue: 10,0:13:17.43,0:13:18.69,dialog,,0,0,0,,Baik.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:18.69,0:13:19.98,dialog,,0,0,0,,An!
Dialogue: 10,0:13:20.74,0:13:23.61,dialog,,0,0,0,,Mari sama-sama berusaha.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:25.47,0:13:27.61,dialog,,0,0,0,,Ba-Baiklah, aku pamit...
Dialogue: 10,0:13:27.61,0:13:28.37,dialog,,0,0,0,,Eh?
Dialogue: 10,0:13:28.37,0:13:30.14,dialog,,0,0,0,,Sa-Sampai jumpa.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:31.07,0:13:33.09,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kamu ini, ya.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:33.09,0:13:34.58,dialog,,0,0,0,,Aku...
Dialogue: 10,0:13:36.43,0:13:38.71,dialog,,0,0,0,,Akan berusaha. Lihat aku, ya.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:41.65,0:13:42.88,dialog,,0,0,0,,Aku tidak akan kalah.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:42.88,0:13:44.29,dialog,,0,0,0,,Aku juga.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:44.29,0:13:46.31,dialog,,0,0,0,,Misaki, ayo pulang.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:46.31,0:13:47.38,dialog,,0,0,0,,Baik.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:47.38,0:13:49.47,dialog,,0,0,0,,Sampai jumpa.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:53.43,0:13:54.93,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kamu...
Dialogue: 10,0:13:54.94,0:13:57.16,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kenapa kamu ada di sini?
Dialogue: 10,0:13:57.16,0:14:00.76,dialog,,0,0,0,,Aku mengajak anggota cowok\Nmakan ramen bersama.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:00.76,0:14:03.41,dialog,,0,0,0,,Waduh, semua sudah berkumpul, ya.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:03.41,0:14:05.65,dialog,,0,0,0,,Selagi ada semua,\Nbagaimana kalau kita lakukan "itu"?
Dialogue: 10,0:14:05.65,0:14:06.98,dialog,,0,0,0,,Apa?
Dialogue: 10,0:14:06.98,0:14:10.87,dialog,,0,0,0,,Persiapan turnamen belum lengkap\Nkalau belum berdoa kepada Dewa.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:11.23,0:14:14.67,dialog,,0,0,0,,Mari pergi mendaki gunung! Gunung!
Dialogue: 10,0:14:21.25,0:14:24.27,dialog,,0,0,0,,Padahal aku hanya datang untuk makan ramen.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:24.27,0:14:27.97,dialog,,0,0,0,,Pak Kichijouji pasti bohong\Nsaat bilang dia ada urusan.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:27.97,0:14:31.18,dialog,,0,0,0,,Orang satu itu memang tidak asyik.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:31.18,0:14:33.68,dialog,,0,0,0,,Dia pasti tidak ingin menaiki tangga.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:33.68,0:14:36.68,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kenapa kuilnya jauh banget, sih?
Dialogue: 10,0:14:36.97,0:14:40.43,dialog,,0,0,0,,Sekali jalan sekitar 40 menit,\Nsemangat, ya.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:41.18,0:14:44.69,dialog,,0,0,0,,Omong-omong,\Nbagaimana seminar di kelas siaran?
Dialogue: 10,0:14:44.97,0:14:46.65,dialog,,0,0,0,,Senior tidak perlu cemas.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:46.65,0:14:48.95,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kami menghabiskan waktu secara produktif.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:49.43,0:14:53.45,dialog,,0,0,0,,Hal yang membuatku gelisah\Njuga sudah terselesaikan.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:53.77,0:14:55.03,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kalau Akiyama?
Dialogue: 10,0:14:55.03,0:14:58.87,dialog,,0,0,0,,Ini kali pertama aku mengikuti\Nsebuah acara ekskul.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:58.87,0:15:02.54,dialog,,0,0,0,,Bagaimana bilangnya, ya?\NIni pengalaman baru.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:02.74,0:15:04.13,dialog,,0,0,0,,Aku senang.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:04.13,0:15:06.07,dialog,,0,0,0,,Bagus, dong.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:06.29,0:15:10.68,dialog,,0,0,0,,Meski begitu...\NHaruyama terlihat tidak baik-baik saja.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:18.25,0:15:19.87,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kalian duluan saja.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:26.49,0:15:27.72,dialog,,0,0,0,,Hana.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:27.72,0:15:29.28,dialog,,0,0,0,,Hadir!
Dialogue: 10,0:15:29.57,0:15:32.07,dialog,,0,0,0,,Apa terjadi sesuatu saat latihan tadi?
Dialogue: 10,0:15:32.07,0:15:35.03,dialog,,0,0,0,,Tidak terjadi apa-apa...
Dialogue: 10,0:15:37.29,0:15:42.92,dialog,,0,0,0,,Maaf. Apa Senior mau mendengarkan?
Dialogue: 10,0:15:44.58,0:15:46.63,dialog,,0,0,0,,Senior Hiiragidani berkata bahwa
Dialogue: 10,0:15:46.63,0:15:49.94,dialog,,0,0,0,,orang yang bisa maju\Nke tingkat nasional itu terbatas.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:49.94,0:15:53.68,dialog,,0,0,0,,Dia memintaku membulatkan tekad\Nuntuk bersaing dengan para senior...
Dialogue: 10,0:15:54.49,0:15:57.68,dialog,,0,0,0,,Mungkin aku tidak ingin menyadari itu.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:57.68,0:16:02.94,dialog,,0,0,0,,Aku hanya memikirkan ingin pergi\Nke tingkat nasional bersama semuanya.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:03.18,0:16:05.98,dialog,,0,0,0,,Ternyata kalau ada yang lolos\Nke tingkat nasional,
Dialogue: 10,0:16:05.98,0:16:09.87,dialog,,0,0,0,,itu artinya ada orang yang gagal.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:09.87,0:16:11.45,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kamu benar.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:12.81,0:16:14.76,dialog,,0,0,0,,Ternyata...
Dialogue: 10,0:16:14.76,0:16:16.45,dialog,,0,0,0,,Memang seperti itu, ya.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:21.16,0:16:23.96,dialog,,0,0,0,,Lihat, ada bunga jeruk Tachibana.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:30.21,0:16:34.87,dialog,,0,0,0,,Di bulan Mei, kala harumnya\Nbunga jeruk Tachibana semerbak,
Dialogue: 10,0:16:34.87,0:16:38.47,dialog,,0,0,0,,kembali terbayang wangi\Ndi lengan baju seseorang dari masa lalu.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:40.65,0:16:43.48,dialog,,0,0,0,,"Bulan Mei" di sini adalah\Nbulan Juni di saat ini.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:43.69,0:16:47.50,dialog,,0,0,0,,Artinya, saat mencium wangi bunga\Njeruk Tachibana yang mekar di musim ini,
Dialogue: 10,0:16:47.50,0:16:52.99,dialog,,0,0,0,,kamu akan teringat pada wangi sitrus dari\Nlengan baju seseorang yang dekat denganmu.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:52.99,0:16:55.89,dialog,,0,0,0,,Orang zaman dahulu\Nbiasa membakar dupa dekat pakaian,
Dialogue: 10,0:16:55.89,0:17:02.50,dialog,,0,0,0,,jadi teringat pada seseorang saat mencium\Naroma yang sama itu hal yang lumrah.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:03.54,0:17:06.47,dialog,,0,0,0,,Aku mengerti perasaan Hana.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:06.47,0:17:09.61,dialog,,0,0,0,,Karena aku sudah disadarkan\Nsetahun yang lalu.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:09.61,0:17:10.50,dialog,,0,0,0,,Eh?
Dialogue: 10,0:17:10.50,0:17:15.25,dialog,,0,0,0,,Tahun lalu, saat aku tahu hanya Mizuki\Nyang lolos ke tingkat nasional...
Dialogue: 10,0:17:15.25,0:17:17.72,dialog,,0,0,0,,Jujur saja, aku frustrasi.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:17.72,0:17:21.47,dialog,,0,0,0,,Padahal aku yang lebih berpengalaman\Ndi Ekskul Penyiaran.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:21.58,0:17:25.72,dialog,,0,0,0,,Perasaan ingin mendukung\Ndan frustrasi pun bercampur aduk.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:25.72,0:17:27.44,dialog,,0,0,0,,Senior...
Dialogue: 10,0:17:28.14,0:17:33.19,dialog,,0,0,0,,"Larilah, Melos",\Nitu adalah bahan bacaan N-Kon tahun itu.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:33.51,0:17:38.05,dialog,,0,0,0,,Tak lama setelah turnamen Kyoto berakhir,\Nteks itu muncul di buku pelajaran.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:38.05,0:17:39.83,dialog,,0,0,0,,Saat membuka buku pelajaran,
Dialogue: 10,0:17:40.11,0:17:43.33,dialog,,0,0,0,,aku mendengarnya kembali.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:45.36,0:17:49.52,dialog,,0,0,0,,Seseorang sedang menantikanku.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:50.27,0:17:55.09,dialog,,0,0,0,,Ia tidak pernah meragukanku,\Ndan menantikan kehadiranku kembali.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:55.96,0:17:58.84,dialog,,0,0,0,,Dia percaya padaku.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:59.17,0:18:03.10,dialog,,0,0,0,,Hidupku tidaklah berharga.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:03.49,0:18:09.32,dialog,,0,0,0,,Namun, sekarang bukan saatnya\Nmencari pengampunan lewat kematian.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:09.56,0:18:12.73,dialog,,0,0,0,,Aku harus buktikan bahwa aku layak\Nmenerima kepercayaannya.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:15.81,0:18:17.86,dialog,,0,0,0,,Itulah yang terpenting saat ini.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:20.37,0:18:22.91,dialog,,0,0,0,,Larilah, Melos!
Dialogue: 10,0:18:29.12,0:18:31.63,dialog,,0,0,0,,Pembacaan yang hebat itu
Dialogue: 10,0:18:31.63,0:18:35.01,dialog,,0,0,0,,mungkin sama seperti wangi\Nbunga jeruk Tachibana.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:35.01,0:18:37.32,dialog,,0,0,0,,Ketika teks dan pembacanya\Nsaling berkaitan,
Dialogue: 10,0:18:37.32,0:18:40.47,dialog,,0,0,0,,dan otomatis tertanam\Ndalam ingatan pendengarnya.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:40.96,0:18:43.29,dialog,,0,0,0,,Mizuki itu sangat berbakat.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:43.29,0:18:45.37,dialog,,0,0,0,,Sudah sejak awal.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:45.37,0:18:49.86,dialog,,0,0,0,,Saat menyadari itu,\Nkegundahan dalam hatiku sirna,
Dialogue: 10,0:18:49.86,0:18:52.36,dialog,,0,0,0,,dan tekadku sudah mantap.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:52.36,0:18:58.03,dialog,,0,0,0,,Apa itu artinya Senior Ryouko\Ntidak keberatan kalah dari Senior Mizuki?
Dialogue: 10,0:18:58.63,0:19:00.96,dialog,,0,0,0,,Bukan.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:01.21,0:19:04.12,dialog,,0,0,0,,Pembacaan Mizuki memang luar biasa.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:04.12,0:19:05.67,dialog,,0,0,0,,Meski begitu,
Dialogue: 10,0:19:05.67,0:19:09.83,dialog,,0,0,0,,pembacaanku juga\Npunya daya tarik yang berbeda.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:10.36,0:19:14.25,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kurasa pembacaanku tidak kalah darinya.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:15.01,0:19:18.17,dialog,,0,0,0,,Aku coba mencintai pembacaanku sendiri.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:18.18,0:19:20.88,dialog,,0,0,0,,Manuskrip yang kupilih.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:21.32,0:19:26.35,dialog,,0,0,0,,Terserah jika ingin membandingkan dengan\Norang lain, atau apa pun hasilnya nanti.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:26.85,0:19:31.35,dialog,,0,0,0,,Percayalah bahwa pembacaanmu itu\Nadalah usaha terbaikmu.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:31.87,0:19:35.11,dialog,,0,0,0,,Aku yakin itulah\Nyang dimaksud dengan "tekad".
Dialogue: 10,0:19:42.86,0:19:44.56,dialog,,0,0,0,,Sampai!
Dialogue: 10,0:19:44.56,0:19:45.49,dialog,,0,0,0,,Ya.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:58.36,0:20:00.63,dialog,,0,0,0,,Begini...
Dialogue: 10,0:20:03.78,0:20:06.38,dialog,,0,0,0,,Senior Mizuki, aku...
Dialogue: 10,0:20:16.89,0:20:20.99,dialog,,0,0,0,,Aku juga sudah membulatkan tekad!
Dialogue: 10,0:20:28.05,0:20:29.81,dialog,,0,0,0,,Bagus.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:39.18,0:20:42.76,dialog,,0,0,0,,Semoga Ekskul Penyiaran kita\Nbisa maju ke tingkat nasional!
Dialogue: 10,0:20:47.01,0:20:49.36,dialog,,0,0,0,,Sip. Persiapannya sudah rampung.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:49.36,0:20:50.77,dialog,,0,0,0,,Maaf...
Dialogue: 10,0:20:51.25,0:20:55.77,dialog,,0,0,0,,Aku diminta Pak Kichijouji membeli ini.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:59.83,0:21:01.92,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kenapa kelulusan?
Dialogue: 10,0:21:02.16,0:21:05.03,dialog,,0,0,0,,Karena hanya ini yang mirip-mirip.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:06.52,0:21:09.61,dialog,,0,0,0,,Harus dijaga baik-baik supaya tidak hilang.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:12.54,0:21:15.71,dialog,,0,0,0,,Selagi di sini,\Nayo berfoto untuk kenang-kenangan!
Dialogue: 10,0:21:17.63,0:21:19.30,dialog,,0,0,0,,Natsue, ke sini lagi sedikit.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:20.01,0:21:21.24,dialog,,0,0,0,,Senior, sini.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:22.41,0:21:23.97,dialog,,0,0,0,,Yuk. Aku foto, ya.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:24.89,0:21:27.78,dialog,,0,0,0,,Baiklah. Senyum!
